{
  "stem": "20021.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 402.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, the Jews, when we left, told us we haven't given up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And indeed, we came to the border.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the last night, this was like 6 o'clock in the evening, did the guards changed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And a new soldier came, a young soldier.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I never saw him before.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He came, and he took us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he didn't say a word.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He brings us to the border.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he says, listen, you-- I will give a shot in the air, which is the signal I'm supposed to alert the German side to come, and come and pick you up.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But you, as soon as you hear me giving that shot, you turn around and you go this way, and you run this way.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And gave us exactly the description how to go to a village, and gave us a description in that village of a house where there was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he's waiting for you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And this must have been prearranged [SOB] [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And really, it's-- it's-- I'm crying when I hear that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And this was prearranged by those Jews back in-- [CRYING] And that's how it happened we came to that house.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there was-- among us was one girl, and she had three children that she kind of adopted.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were from ghettos that they-- that they-- they managed to run and come to Romania.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they somehow survived in Romania, and were finally caught or whatever also this way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "No, they were-- must have been Hungarian, but I never met these people before.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I never met this girl before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "She was Romanian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She spoke Romanian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "How she got into this group, I don't even know, because that's just the first time we met them, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And this guy gave that shot.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
